# Complete DevOps Platform Setup Runbook


To avoid the eks cluster being created when you havent completed your Jenkins configuration, ensure  that inside your terraform.tfvars you have (Note: You will still change it later to true when you are done with your Jenkins and Sonarqube configurations)

enable_eks  = false 

Also inside your jenkinsfile 

for the first ci build if you do not want to push to the EKS cluster yet, ensure 

Deploy to EKS = false 

and when you want to deploy into the cluster change it to true

# Overview

This document covers the FULL setup process for:

* Terraform modular infrastructure
* Jenkins EC2 provisioning
* Custom Jenkins Docker image
* SonarQube integration
* GitHub integration
* ECR integration
* Quality Gates
* Webhooks
* Trivy security scanning
* Optional EKS deployment

This guide is written step-by-step for future reuse.

