# Step 32 — Verify Jenkinsfile Quality Gate Stage

Verify Jenkinsfile contains:

```groovy
stage('Quality Gate') {
    steps {
        timeout(time: 5, unit: 'MINUTES') {
            waitForQualityGate abortPipeline: true
        }
    }
}
```

This makes Jenkins:

* wait for Sonar analysis
* fail build if quality gate fails

